        "mmx_texteditor": {
            "component_code": "mmx-text-editor",
            "item_code": "mmx_texteditor",
            "settings": {
                "_flex": {
                    "flex_version": 10.1103,
                    "settings_version": "10.11.03"
                },
                "advanced": {
                    "spacing": {
                        "top": {
                            "value": -50
                        }
                    }
                },
                "content": {
                    "value": "<div class=\"charge-pipe-features\" style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;\">\r\n    <h2 style=\"color: #004aad; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold;\">Sinister Diesel Coolant Filtration Kits</h2>\r\n    \r\n    <h3 style=\"color: #222; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Features</h3>\r\n    <ul style=\"list-style: disc; margin-left: 20px;\">\r\n        <li>CNC Machined 6061 Aluminum Filter Block</li>\r\n        <li>High Strength, Abrasion Resistant Silicon Hoses</li>\r\n        <li>Extends the life of your Water Pump, Oil Cooler, and EGR Cooler</li>\r\n        <li>Maintains optimal coolant flow as this is a bypass filtration kit</li>\r\n        <li>Installation Hardware & Instructions</li>\r\n    </ul>\r\n\r\n    <h3 style=\"color: #222; font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;\">Benefits</h3>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        Coolant plays a crucial role in keeping your truck\u2019s engine at optimal temperatures. Excessive heat can lead to catastrophic failure, making proper coolant maintenance essential. With a quality filtration system, you can drive with confidence knowing that harmful contaminants\u2014such as casting sand, metal shavings, rust, and mineral deposits\u2014are continuously filtered out, protecting your engine for the long haul.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        Built with high-quality materials, our coolant filtration kits are engineered for long-lasting durability. The high strength silicone hoses are durable and abrasion resistant, while our presealed fittings insure leak-free operation.  \r\n    </p>\r\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px;\">\r\n        The Sinister Blue powder-coated finish isn\u2019t just for looks\u2014it provides enhanced durability while giving your engine bay a sleek, high-quality appearance. Unlike brands that cut corners, our signature color stands for quality and American craftsmanship, ensuring your aftermarket upgrade is built to last and won\u2019t leave you stranded when you need it most.\r\n    </p>\r\n</div>"
                }
            }
        },
